The paper deals with image captioning, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep neural networks for image captioning also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the analysis of semantic information, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
